{{Quote|Some people believe that... if you say your real name aloud. The swamp demon will hear it and claim you!|[[Darovit|Tomcat]]|<ref name="Jedi vs. Sith 1">[[Jedi vs. Sith 1|''Jedi vs. Sith'' 1]]</ref>}}
The '''swamp demon''' was a mythological [[Demon/Legends|demon]] on [[Somov Rit]]. According to legend, he would swallow anyone who said their real name aloud. This led to the Somovian practice of everyone using nicknames.

